Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake

Class DataLakeFile

java.lang.Object
java.io.File
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake.DataLakeFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
fi.aalto.scicomp.zipper.FileDescriptor, Serializable, Comparable<File>
public class DataLakeFile extends File implements fi.aalto.scicomp.zipper.FileDescriptor
This is a wrapper for a File in the datalake. While the datalake has unspecified filenames This wrapper allows associating a filename with such a randomly generated filename In order to provide a human readable piece of information.
Author:
Thomas Pfau

      Basic constructor given a real filename, the original Filename and the format of the file contents.
      Parameters:
      dataLakePath - the actual location of the file
      pathInLake - the path within the lake
      originalFileName - the Name this file originally had (as the path likely points to a random file name)
      mimeFormat - the format of the file contents.
